Tr57809.@label: Figure 1. The phylogeny of Phoma lingam and Phoma betae, the type species of Phoma sections Plenodomus and Pilosa, based on the strict consensus tree from a Bayesian analysis of 48 LSU/SSU sequences. The Bayesian posterior probabilities are given at the nodes. The tree was rooted to Sporormiella minima (CBS 524.50).
